      <quote xml:lang="he"><p>י דפים מכת אלאנואר לקרקסאני, בלוים בחלק, ואולי הם מב כי. / Bunde Number: 508</p></quote>
      <persName ref="">Avraham Harkavy</persName>
      <note xml:lang="en"><p>The “Harkavy-Cards” were the foundation for his handwritten four-volume inventory of the Yevr.-Arab. section of the Second Firkovich Collection. This inventory is today held at the Vernadsky Library of the Ukrainian Academy of Sciences in Kiev, and also served as basis of the library’s card catalog prepared over the years by Harkavy, F. Kokovtzov, R. Ravrebe, A. Vasilev and V. Lebedev. </p></note>
